<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>数据库 - 分类 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/categories/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93/</link><description>数据库 - 分类 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/categories/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>MySQL存储引擎</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93/mysql%E5%AD%98%E5%82%A8%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93/mysql%E5%AD%98%E5%82%A8%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="mysql存储引擎">MySQL存储引擎</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：InnoDB通过聚簇索引组织数据，通过MVCC实现无锁读，通过行锁和间隙锁实现并发控制，是MySQL生产环境的事实标准；MyISAM已逐步被InnoDB取代，仅在特殊读多写少场景考虑。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="innodb通过聚簇索引mvcc行锁三大机制实现高并发事务安全是mysql生产环境的首选存储引擎">InnoDB通过聚簇索引、MVCC、行锁三大机制实现高并发事务安全，是MySQL生产环境的首选存储引擎</h2>
<h3 id="innodb核心特性">InnoDB核心特性</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>特性</th>
          <th>实现</th>
          <th>优势</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>聚簇索引</td>
          <td>主键索引即数据</td>
          <td>主键查询快，范围查询高效</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>MVCC</td>
          <td>undo log + 事务ID</td>
          <td>读不阻塞写，写不阻塞读</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>行级锁</td>
          <td>记录锁 + 间隙锁</td>
          <td>并发度高</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>外键</td>
          <td>支持级联操作</td>
          <td>数据完整性</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>崩溃恢复</td>
          <td>Redo Log + Double Write</td>
          <td>数据不丢失</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>缓冲池</td>
          <td>内存缓存数据和索引</td>
          <td>减少磁盘IO</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="mvcc多版本并发控制">MVCC：多版本并发控制</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">MVCC核心：每行数据有两个隐藏列
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">DB_TRX_ID（6字节）：最后修改该行的事务ID
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">DB_ROLL_PTR（7字节）：指向undo log的回滚指针
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Read View（快照）：事务开始时创建的一致性视图
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - creator_trx_id：创建该视图的事务ID
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - up_limit_id：活跃事务最小ID
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - low_limit_id：即将分配的下一个事务ID
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - trx_ids：活跃事务ID列表
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">可见性判断：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  1. DB_TRX_ID == creator_trx_id：可见（自己修改的）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  2. DB_TRX_ID &lt; up_limit_id：可见（事务已提交）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  3. DB_TRX_ID &gt;= low_limit_id：不可见（事务未开始）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  4. DB_TRX_ID在trx_ids中：不可见（事务活跃未提交）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  5. 其他情况：可见</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>InnoDB的三种行记录格式</strong>：</p>]]></description></item><item><title>MySQL瓶颈与扩展</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93/mysql%E6%89%A9%E5%B1%95/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93/mysql%E6%89%A9%E5%B1%95/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="mysql瓶颈与扩展">MySQL瓶颈与扩展</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：MySQL单库的瓶颈在CPU、内存、磁盘IO和连接数四个维度，扩展路径从读写分离到分库分表逐步递进，每种方案都在一致性、复杂度和成本之间做权衡。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="mysql单库存在cpu内存磁盘连接数四重瓶颈扩展路径为读写分离垂直拆分水平分表分库分表">MySQL单库存在CPU、内存、磁盘、连接数四重瓶颈，扩展路径为读写分离→垂直拆分→水平分表→分库分表</h2>
<h3 id="单库瓶颈分析">单库瓶颈分析</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>瓶颈</th>
          <th>表现</th>
          <th>临时解决</th>
          <th>根本解决</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>CPU</td>
          <td>慢查询多、计算密集</td>
          <td>优化SQL、加缓存</td>
          <td>读写分离、分库</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>内存</td>
          <td>缓冲池不足、频繁换页</td>
          <td>增大内存</td>
          <td>分库分散压力</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>磁盘IO</td>
          <td>iowait高、磁盘满</td>
          <td>SSD、加索引</td>
          <td>分表、归档</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>连接数</td>
          <td>Too many connections</td>
          <td>增大max_connections</td>
          <td>连接池、分库</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="读写分离一主多从架构">读写分离：一主多从架构</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">写请求 → 主库（Master）→ 异步复制 → 从库（Slave）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">读请求 → 从库1 / 从库2 / 从库N
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">复制方式：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 异步复制：主库写完即返回，延迟小但可能丢数据
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 半同步复制：至少一个从库确认收到binlog才返回
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 组复制（MGR）：Paxos协议，强一致性
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">延迟问题：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 主从延迟导致读取旧数据
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 解决方案：强制走主库（关键读）、延迟阈值告警</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="分库分表水平与垂直拆分">分库分表：水平与垂直拆分</h3>
<p><strong>垂直拆分</strong>：按业务模块拆分</p>]]></description></item><item><title>MySQL索引与优化</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93/mysql%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93/mysql%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="mysql索引与优化">MySQL索引与优化</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：MySQL索引通过B+树实现高效查找，索引设计的核心原则是减少回表、避免全表扫描，EXPLAIN是排查慢SQL的首要工具，理解索引下推和覆盖索引是优化的关键。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="mysql通过b树索引加速查询索引设计决定查询性能上限explain是排查sql性能的首要工具">MySQL通过B+树索引加速查询，索引设计决定查询性能上限，EXPLAIN是排查SQL性能的首要工具</h2>
<h3 id="b树索引结构与查询原理">B+树索引结构与查询原理</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">聚簇索引（主键索引）：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        [10, 20, 30]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">       /     |     \
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  [5,7,9] [15,18] [25,28,29]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">     ↓        ↓         ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   数据行   数据行    数据行
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">特点：叶子节点存储完整数据行，按主键排序
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
